dct_description_sm: Undated map showing layout of Chester borough with only major streets named. Only landmarks shown are a furnace with mill and approximately a dozen residences with names of homeowners. Only other note states that lots are 50 feet wide by 150 feet deep and that main streets are 75 feet and side streets 50 feet wide
